description:
Join the live stream of the 61st General Conference Session being held in St. Louis, Missouri, USA.

This morning following a digital music concert, Dwain Esmond will present a worship message entitled, "The Rest of the Story." Dwain Esmond is an author, editor, and speaker, and currently holds the position of Associate Director at Ellen G. White Estate, Inc. 

Following the worship, we will move into our morning business session. You can access the session agenda here: https://www.gcsession.org/session-agenda/

Follow our church social media accounts to get more informational and inspirational posts throughout this week: 

ANN Website: https://adventist.news/ 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/adventistchurch/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/adventistchurch/ 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheAdventistChurch
